d reveal some interesting design insights that are\ndifferent from conventional contention-based communication network assuming the\nWDs are powered with unlimited energy supplies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Mar 2017 01:00:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-20"}
